*************************************************
* Cosmic Ray tagger Offline UTilities in pythON *
*************************************************

The software needs the same miniconda environment as for LARDON

To run the code on data :

--> just one day of data 
python crouton.py -day <YYYYMMDD> 

--> over several days
python crouton.py -from <YYYYMMDD> -to <YYYYMMDD>

If you want an output file (to be done) -out <optional name>

---
(x, y, z) axes conventions is the same as in LARDON